{"tid":867732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又贏！中國第3季經濟增長放緩至6.5%　創9年半新低","createTime":"2018-10-19T02:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T02:15:07.000Z","uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e20695d27d41134d86bb79ac44401df6743db9e8","tid":867732,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:07:50.000Z","msg":"中國國家統計局公布，中國第3季經濟增長進一步放緩至6.5%，創9年半新低，並低於市場預期的6.6%。經濟增長連續兩季減慢，較第2季減慢0.2個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n至於今年首3季經濟按年增長6.7%。<br />\n<br />\n統計局表示，首3季經濟運行在合理區間，保持整體平穩、穩中有進發展勢頭。不過，外部挑戰變數明顯增加，國內結構調整陣痛繼續出現，經濟下行壓力加大。中央會著力擴大有效需求，落實穩就業、穩外貿及穩投資等政策，實現全年經濟社會發展目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1423728-20181019.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1423728-20181019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=75b57937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1423728-20181019.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e5435f50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1423728-20181019.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2baaa921e4034006285d18b358b33ff18b12de25","tid":867732,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:11:22.000Z","msg":"中國國家統計局公佈，中國第三季GDP按年增長6.5%，較預期的6.6%略低，前值為增長6.7%。首三季GDP增長6.7%。<br />\n<br />\n中國9月規模以上工業增加值按年升5.8%，預期為6.1%。社會消費品零售總額按年增長9.2%，預期為9%。中國9月發電量按年增長4.6%，低於8月的7.3%按年增幅；中國1至9月全國房地產開發投資按年增長9.9%，1至8月為10.1%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181019/58810481\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F58810481&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c4b5f2e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181019%2F58810481&h=c86506b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181019/58810481</a>"},{"pid":"608ea48f9a611f7b1e7d7ec812aa7ce0f6c20acc","tid":867732,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:13:30.000Z","msg":"d數據假架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63d3340e6df8db7a9123ef1e80f92a3343a4fd16","tid":867732,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:15:07.000Z","msg":"仲係正數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}